--- !u!114 &610160112
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 610160107}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0cd2ba4c2c3b32445adbe449f702dd96, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
    dialogueLines:
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: Oh hello?
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: I didn't know you could see me!
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: But you're still alive?
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: That means you entered another realm?
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: Yeah if you took the lift that can happen sometimes
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: That means taking the stairs back won't help you escape it.
    - character:
        name: Morley
        icon: {fileID: -134938495, guid: 50312a879e37fb44f8b4e0ccf560d16a, type: 3}
      line: You need to pick up a magic book with the code for the lift to go back
        to the real world! Just have to search around, I am sure it's here!
  context: {fileID: 1725207796}
